{"tid":1789031,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"點解波台手足呀媽會生左呢個弱智出黎(:P)","createTime":"2019-12-19T07:14:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T18:04:35.000Z","uid":44748,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bde04e498e10004bb9d3f5183ee8aad662785c48","tid":1789031,"uid":44748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T07:14:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1788567/page/1?order=score\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1788567/page/1?order=score</a><br />\n(#62)留言<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dio1NjG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdio1NjG.png&h=ed70fc3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先要中文解釋呢2個字:騰空(騰左4,5秒空 )<br />\n騰空係由起腳一刻到落地一刻既成個動作<br />\n<br />\n然後係物埋角度解釋:<br />\n跳起既時間係會比跌落黎既時間長高多<br />\n當中包括action &amp; reaction 反地心吸力 同地地心吸力 既原理<br />\n示意圖:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M7sRp6f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM7sRp6f.png&h=6a8a7206&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔明點解仲有超過40人讚佢搞到好似以為少過1秒好啱咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通認為佢啱既都你弱智?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跌落黎果下少過1秒係冇錯<br />\n但由雙腳發力離地去到最高點果刻係可以超過1秒<br />\n真係唔知點解波台手足呀媽會生左呢個弱智出黎(<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b89586de4dcba22b8e2687932c0772d007cbca0a","tid":1789031,"uid":37827,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T07:20:53.000Z","msg":"答案係!! 陳國邦 (李斯) <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JJebjw3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJJebjw3.jpg&h=a0ee34e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2Laz5t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2Laz5t.jpg&h=b15df2e2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n因為去沙灘唔昅女啫係silly 癡線 冇可能會發生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSilly發音就係 see Li 斯李<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而我地華人社會 習慣將last name 擺前面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以!!!!!!! 答案就係李斯喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而做過李斯嘅TVB藝員就係得陳國邦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以!!!!!!!!!!!!!答案係!!!!!!!!!陳國邦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VB5YJY3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVB5YJY3.jpg&h=84f4867c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n輕鬆 謝謝大家"},{"pid":"e87f6e711b7577caa3182af884e17da18a0a9d50","tid":1789031,"uid":5475,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T07:28:38.000Z","msg":"睇撚死你冇撚讀過phy la<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e8a8eb4f11f035802aeb1a69b973c90a55e536","tid":1789031,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T07:43:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfGlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=45694a72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=